      passage: `Microplastics are a common pollutant in large masses of water like glaciers. High concentrations and ______ among particles—variations in size, shape, and material—make it onerous to comprehensively classify the microplastics in a water sample, so Kutay Icoz et al. are exploring a device to help quickly and accurately identify certain characteristics.`,
